Package info6205.Graph

Class EdgeWeightedListGraph<NodeValue,NodeKeyValue,EdgeWeight extends Comparable<EdgeWeight>>

java.lang.Object
info6205.Graph.EdgeWeightedListGraph<NodeValue,NodeKeyValue,EdgeWeight>
Type Parameters:
NodeValue - Type of value the Node or vertices hold for this graph
NodeKeyValue - Type of unique ID for a node or vertices for this graph
EdgeWeight - Type of Edge Weight the edge will represent for this graph, this needs to implement Comparable
All Implemented Interfaces:
WeightedAdjacencyListGraph<NodeValue,NodeKeyValue,EdgeWeight>
Direct Known Subclasses:
UndirectedEdgeWeighedListGraph
public abstract class EdgeWeightedListGraph<NodeValue,NodeKeyValue,EdgeWeight extends Comparable<EdgeWeight>> extends Object implements WeightedAdjacencyListGraph<NodeValue,NodeKeyValue,EdgeWeight>
This abstract class represents Weighted Edge Graph, whether this is a directed or undirected graphs depends on its implementation
